title: Can you see it? Res Lease in Kyle. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Located in Kyle, Just a short drive south of Austin.
Kyle is a small, but quickly growing town.
The town offers a great mix of urban and small-town feel, with plenty of restaurants, outdoor fun, and more.
Right when you walk in, you notice how open it feels because of all the windows.
Not only does this home feel huge, it's complete with 3 bedrooms, and 2.5 bathrooms.
The open kitchen boasts wood cabinetry, recessed lighting, a stand-alone kitchen island, and state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances, sure to make any home chef happy!
The house has a bonus room that can be used as an office, 2 living spaces and tons of storage!
The primary bedroom has plenty of windows, ceiling fan, large walk-in closet, and ensuite bath with double vanity, soaking tub and spacious stand up shower!
More wonderful features include a full-sized washer/ dryer, a privately fenced backyard, and 2-car attached garage!
Pool, sports area with volleyball and basketball, large park and playground close by!
All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.
Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.
Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC
